<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.8">
<l>veḷḷaip puravit tērvi cayaṟkāy viṟalviyūkam</l>
<l>viḷḷa cintuk kōṉvi ḻavūrnta vimalaṉūr</l>
<l>koḷḷaik koḻumī ṉuṇkuru kōṭip peṭaiyōṭum</l>
<l>naḷḷak kamalat tēṟa lukukkum naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the flawless one who drove a chariot with white horses for Vijaya,</l>
<l>So that the formidable army scattered and the king of Sindhu fell,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr where a heron with its mate, chasing a school of fat fish [for] food,</l>
<l>Scatters nectar from the center of the lotuses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
